org.drip.validation.quantile

Class PlottingPosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.validation.quantile.PlottingPosition

  • public class PlottingPosition
extends java.lang.Object
    PlottingPosition holds the Order Statistic Ordinal and the Quantile corresponding to a Plotting Position.
